title: 6 GiB of MP3s from Punk to WTF
description:
A personal collection a rather eclectic & fucked up selection of tunes. Obviously I like some more than others, but it is funny to see some of the queer shit people will have in their personal collections. Some of the shit just does not seem like it belongs!
